### toate
GET http://localhost:8081/api/coaches

### creeaza coach
POST http://localhost:8081/api/coaches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex"
}

### update
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/coaches/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria D. (update)"
}

